-street-brewing-celebrates-two-years-opens-taproom|accessdate=19 January 2015}}</ref>\n|Atlanta Beverage Company/Modern Hops\n|-\n| [[Coastal Empire Beer Co.]] || Savannah || 2011 || Brewery || 1,300\n|Savannah Distribution\n|-\n|[[Creature Comforts Brewing Co.|Creature Comforts]]<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Athens\n|2014\n|Brewery\n|50,000+\n|Savannah Distributing\n|-\n|Dry County<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Kennesaw\n|2015\n|Brewery\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n| Eagle Creek Brewing Company || Statesboro || 2013 || Brewery || 4,500<ref>{{cite web|title=Brewery Spotlight: Eagle Creek Brewing Company|url=http://www.bandbbeverageco.com/2014/09/09/brewery-spotlight-eagle-creek-brewing-company/|accessdate=19 January 2015}}</ref>\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n|Eventide<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta\n|2015\n|Brewery\n|\n|United Distributors\n|-\n|Fannin Brewing<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Blue Ridge\n|2012\n|Brewery\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n|Gate City<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Roswell\n|2016\n|Brewery\n|\n|United Distributors\n|-\n|Gordon Biersch<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta & Buckhead\n|\n|Brewery\n|\n|\n|-\n|Grumpy Old Men Brewery<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Blue Ridge\n|2012\n|Brewpub\n|\n|Savannah Distributing\n|-\n|Hop Alley (CLOSED)<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Alpharetta\n|\n|Brewery\n|\n|\n|-\n|Iron Monger Brewery<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Marietta\n|2016\n|Brewery\n|\n|National Distributors\n|-\n|Jailhouse Brewing<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Hampton\n|2009\n|Brewery\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n| Jekyll Brewing || Alpharetta || 2011 || Brewery || 7,500<ref name=\"clatl.com\">{{cite web|title=Georgia's top 10 craft breweries by production |url=http://clatl.com/omnivore/archives/2015/03/31/georgias-top-10-craft-breweries-by-production|accessdate=27 April 2015}}</ref>\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n|Left Nut Brewing Company<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Gainesville\n|2016\n|Brewery\n|\n|Leon Farmer & Company\n|-\n|Macon Beer Company<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Macon\n|2013\n|Brewery\n|\n|Bibb Distributing\n|-\n|Max Lager\u2019s Wood-Fired Grill & Brewery<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta\n|\n|Brewpub\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n| [[Monday Night Brewing]] || Atlanta || 2011 || Brewery || 7,500<ref name=\"clatl.com\"/>\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n| [[Moon River Brewing Company]] || Savannah || 1999 || Brewpub || Unknown\n|Savannah Distributing\n|-\n|Oconoee Brewing Company<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.oconeebrewingco.com/|title=Oconee Brewing Company|website=Oconee Brewing Company|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-26}}</ref>\n|Greensboro\n|2017\n|Brewpub\n|\n|Georgia Crown Distribution Company\n|-\n|Omaha Brewing Company<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Omaha\n|2014\n|Brewery\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n|Orpheus Brewing<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta\n|2014\n|Brewery\n|\n|United Distributors\n|-\n| Piedmont Brewery & Kitchen || Macon || 2016 || Brewpub || Unknown<ref>{{cite web|title=Excitement brews for Piedmont|url=http://11thhouronline.com/2016/05/16/excitement-brews-for-piedmont-the-brewery-kitchen-to-open-this-fall/|accessdate=1 June 2016}}</ref>    \n|Modern Hops\n|-\n|Pontoon Brewing<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta\n|\n|Brewery\n|\n|Georgia Crown Distributing\n|-\n|Printer's Ale Manufacturing Company<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://printers-ale.com/|title=Printer's Ale Mfg Co - Home|website=Printer's Ale Mfg Co.|language=en-US|access-date=2019-12-30}}</ref>\n|Carrollton\n|2017\n|Brewery\n|\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\nLaGrange Grocery\n|-\n|Atlanta Brewing Co. (previously: Red Brick Brewing Company)<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Atlanta\n|1993\n|Brewery\n|\n|United Distributors\n|-\n| Red Hare Brewing Company || Marietta || 2011 || Brewery || 8,000<ref name=\"clatl.com\"/>\n|Atlanta Beverage Company\n|-\n|Reformation Brewery\n|Woodstock\n|2012\n|Brewery\n|5,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/BeerGuysRadio/videos/1905889756306535/ |title=Beer Guys Radio - We are LIVE with the Reformation crew|last=Nix|first=Spencer|date=2017-01-05|website=www.facebook.com|publisher=|ac